article.linkText: Collison's career effort sends Duke packing
article.story: DURHAM, N.C. (AP) -- J.J. Redick scored 23 points on 6-for-8 shooting from 3-point range and No. 2 Duke beat Nike Elite 105-69 Wednesday night in an exhibition. Shavlik Randolph added 18 points and Luol Deng and Shelden Williams each had 17 for the Blue Devils, who open the season Nov. 22 at home against Detroit. Duke never trailed, leading 12-2 behind eight points from Deng. Stan Blackmon led Nike Elite with 22 points.
